We present to you the latest updates to our Translator application which are designed to make your use of the application even more comfortable and efficient: Dark theme and system color palette Improved camera translator interface Improved work of the phrasebook Filtering by languages in favorites and history Overall increase in productivity and user experience Don t miss the chance to update the app and check out all the new features! Thank you for being with us and sharing your impressions!
